# NOTES
# ========================================
# - Public: GET /api/testimonials, GET /api/testimonials/:id
# - Protected: POST, PUT, DELETE
# - Fields: name, email, message, image, rating (1-5), job, clinicName (optional)
# - createdAt is set automatically

